 statement to the former boss you despise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4483210/extras/102f64ed6048cd142f0ef9df9839cb13.poster.avif?t=1776578958\" width=706 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4483210/extras/102f64ed6048cd142f0ef9df9839cb13.webm?t=1776578958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4483210/extras/102f64ed6048cd142f0ef9df9839cb13.mp4?t=1776578958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various events related to the main heroine will occur</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your affection or love rating will increase depending on your choices during the drama</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(Be warned - making wrong choices will raise your criminal coefficient...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additionally, there are many mini-games available</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some help you earn money, while others boost your affection or love ratings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raising your affection or love ratings through these will advance the main story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4483210/extras/171d2f6b8d1315c5fa6b40832ff871b2.poster.avif?t=1776578958\" width=618 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4483210/extras/171d2f6b8d1315c5fa6b40832ff871b2.webm?t=1776578958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4483210/extras/171d2f6b8d1315c5fa6b40832ff871b2.mp4?t=1776578958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\