 an act of revenge slowly changes into something more.<br>As Yuki spends time with Keiko, he gradually finds himself falling for her.<br>Keiko, too, becomes unable to suppress her growing feelings through their interactions.<br>Confess your love and work toward marriage.<br>This is the game’s main storyline.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■ Revenge Route</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Introduce Keiko to a new part-time job in the nightlife industry. <br>Record key moments of her new life and compile them into a video message. <br>Send it as a final statement to the former boss you despise.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4483210/extras/102f64ed6048cd142f0ef9df9839cb13.poster.avif?t=1776578958\" width=706 height=398 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4483210/extras/102f64ed6048cd142f0ef9df9839cb13.webm?t=1776578958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4483210/extras/102f64ed6048cd142f0ef9df9839cb13.mp4?t=1776578958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various events related to the main heroine will occur</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your affection or love rating will increase depending on your choices during the drama</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(Be warned - making wrong choices will raise your criminal coefficient...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additionally, there are many mini-games available</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some help you earn money, while others boost your affection or love ratings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Raising your affection or love ratings through these will advance the main story</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c